  "texts": [
    "In a few of the works, the morphological features of the human brain are utilized for feature extractions.",
    "For example, Murugan et al. (2021) developed a model named DEMentia NETwork (DEMNET) for detecting different stages of dementia.",
    "For identifying particular AD traits from the MRI images CNN is employed.",
    "The proposed model takes into consideration the four phases of dementia and performs a specific diagnosis by generating high quality disease probability maps based on regional brain structure.",
    "It attains an accuracy of 95.23%."
  ],
